column5: A nice 3 bedroom home in safe neighborhood, 8 miles from downtown / 7 miles from Zilker / 20 mins from Airport. Master bed and office will be locked off, but two bedrooms and the rest of the house are available for use while I am out of town. TV's in both living room and single guest room, as well as other standard home amenities to feel comfortable.
column8: All to yourself - Private Home / Two Rooms -SW ATX
